177 A.3d 113 CAROLYN GILLIAM, PLAINTIFF-PETITIONER, v. ATRIUM AT PRINCETON, LLC, T/A ATRIUM HEALTH, DEFENDANT-RESPONDENT.

C-399 September Term 2017

079970 December 8, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002514-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
